<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT85">
<l>toḻileṉakkut tollaimāl taṉṉāma mētta</l>
<l>poḻuteṉakku maṟṟatuvē pōtuṅ kaḻiciṉatta</l>
<l>vallāḷaṉ vāṉarakkōṉ vāli mataṉaḻitta</l>
<l>villāḷaṉ neñcat tuḷaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My occupation is to extol the names of the ancient Māl.</l>
<l>My time shall be spent [doing] that.</l>
<l>The Expert Archer who destroyed the arrogance</l>
<l>of Vālin, the king of monkeys, the mighty one with excessive anger,</l>
<l rend="indent"> is in [my] heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
